<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>View Announcements</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .announcement {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .society {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5688A8;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .date {
            color: #0056b3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .announcement-text {
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>View Announcements</h1>
        <div class="announcement">
            <div class="society">Society Name</div>
            <div class="date">April 18, 2024</div>
            <div class="announcement-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed vitae gravida tortor. Nulla nec enim nec arcu eleifend bibendum.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="announcement">
            <div class="society">Another Society</div>
            <div class="date">April 17, 2024</div>
            <div class="announcement-text">Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Nulla facilisi.</div>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more announcements here -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>
